 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d873b2f2b64529b391c74f39bf7624666ea7ba74","tid":111042,"uid":464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T07:32:26.000Z","msg":"小學點會夠膽唔做功課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有以前小學係朝早就交 交完拎落教員室<br />\n中學就交俾科長姐 好多時都R個科長俾人地果份我抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53641cd965190dfa77db7d51927855b3f4d71c0f","tid":111042,"uid":35315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T07:36:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小學點會夠膽唔做功課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有以前小學係朝早就交 交完拎落教員室<br />\n中學就交俾科長姐 好多時都R個科長俾人地果份我抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好多時上堂個下已經可以做一兩份功課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a487bead8c90431e054e2b25170470936da8ff5f","tid":111042,"uid":1789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T07:40:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小學點會夠膽唔做功課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有以前小學係朝早就交 交完拎落教員室<br />\n中學就交俾科長姐 好多時都R個科長俾人地果份我抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好多時上堂個下已經可以做一兩份功課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n放學前仲有一堂自修定咩功課班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基本上都做曬先翻屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n錯左咪到時抄人答案改正囉<br />\n咁執著做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79dd11b07da95a1e90135afb011c857e45835013","tid":111042,"uid":37753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T07:43:56.000Z","msg":"想當年中學一日九樣功課 上堂專心少少同班frd一路傾一路做 未到放學就做哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n數字黎睇的確誇張 但如果學習氣氛好老師主導得好 對學生係一件好事<br />\n利申：唔支持太多 重質不重量"},{"pid":"b8c46cd37016027b761383495f87be5910adf380","tid":111042,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T07:49:22.000Z","msg":"想當年一日6樣功課都係返到去先抄<br />\n早15分鐘返已經夠"},{"pid":"8f1fd4c81947b4f2ef8db5876c6988ab42be2dab","tid":111042,"uid":71058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T07:50:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜而家既學生唔識分工合作<br />\n小學都算<br />\n中學都唔識抄功課咁真係無得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗冇人唔識抄功課既 <br />\n唔好講到自己識抄功課好似好撚風趣咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f21e2366017a8b378843700356a4e25f25f4d9cc","tid":111042,"uid":35315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T07:50:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小學點會夠膽唔做功課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有以前小學係朝早就交 交完拎落教員室<br />\n中學就交俾科長姐 好多時都R個科長俾人地果份我抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好多時上堂個下已經可以做一兩份功課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n放學前仲有一堂自修定咩功課班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基本上都做曬先翻屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n錯左咪到時抄人答案改正囉<br />\n咁執著做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以問題重心一定係家長唔識教，當年多功課我老豆都係叫我求其做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  錯咗咪睇答案，考試先畀心機"},{"pid":"869cf22a6a9b84b0bf2ae7761ea8b088a890bcc7","tid":111042,"uid":44878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T08:13:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>功課要做架咩<br />\n日日抄功課抄到上u<br />\n只係平時專心少少聽書聽重點已經夠</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">考dse臨急抱佛腳就得<br />\n上到大學底唔好你食硬屎<br />\nYou will pay for it<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></blockquote><br />\n睇咩科啦<br />\n你話science工程個類無得講啦<br />\n其他好多hea讀都有3啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大學除左science果堆<br />\n好多都係一齊reset重開架啦<br />\n中學野有幾可用得返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗依位巴打更specific係指語文底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似之前開過post話上到U因為英文差寫唔到paper，所以依家要努力追hon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於理科專科無讀過，易唔易過3唔評論<br />\n<br />\n但我都係讀同中學無關嘅sosci，都明語文好重要，語文好都幾易過3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40d39dc1eeddd39a97071eef83a59dd177cba6db","tid":111042,"uid":68632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T08:14:37.000Z","msg":"最尾辛苦埋個老豆老母 九成要幫手做<br />\n唔洗做 都要對"},{"pid":"8a1187ac71f4ed41bbfd768450a04e60786f3265","tid":111042,"uid":68632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T08:16:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最尾辛苦埋個老豆老母 九成要幫手做<br />\n唔洗做 都要對</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇錯 以為係小學<br />\n<br />\n中學生應該要發展自己解難能力<br />\n抄得就抄啦"},{"pid":"045ee47d9a96d026ec76fd4bdcf123631082f835","tid":111042,"uid":32479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T08:38:17.000Z","msg":"上面叫人抄功課果啲 不如試下大學都抄功課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d95086825ff21736747d996998142d8c94db897","tid":111042,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T08:45:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上面叫人抄功課果啲 不如試下大學都抄功課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ee055344fe7b896631423076d512f3e4c30b0ec","tid":111042,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T09:14:06.000Z","msg":"小學會做既 <br />\n上到中學一係抄一係欠 <br />\n做晒咁